# CamStream



Simple interface for connect and display the video stream from a camera.



Developed by Aimar Abimayu Pratama (c) 2024



## How To Use



```python

from camstream import camstream

import cv2



cam = cv2.VideoCapture(0)

camstream(cam)

```

